sources.title: The Scar (1948) FILM NOIRüçï JOAN BENNETTüçï PAUL HENREID
sources.description:
Cinematography: John Alton
Stars: Paul Henreid, Joan Bennett , Eduard Franz 
Director: Steve Sekely

Pursued by the gangsters he robbed, a thief murders a lookalike psychiatrist and assumes his identity. In an ironic twist, the dead shrink had bigger problems than his own! Watch for a young Jack Webb as "Bullseye." (a.k.a. The Man Who Killed Himself and Hollow Triumph)
